title: Counter-Strike 1.6 Nation BattleGrounds
description: Site: http://counter-strike16.eu About the Game: Play the world's number 1 online action game. Engage in an incredibly realistic brand of terrorist warfare in this wildly popular team-based game. Ally with teammates to complete strategic missions. Take out enemy sites. Rescue hostages. Your role affects your team's success. Your team's success affects your role. FEATURES: - Release date January 01, 2018 - 100% Clean Rip from Steam GCFs (Game Cache files) - Only ~433MB setup size - Latest engine update (1.1.2.6/2.0.0.0 Jun 15 2009 build 4554) - Dual Protocol (48 + 47) Client - Client could join p47 servers as well as p48 - Dual Protocol (48 + 47) Dedicated Server is also included - Fully working server browser with favorites - Compatible with Latest sXe Injected - Added latest CZ bots modified for CS - Works with Vista/Windows 7 - Playable on LAN and Internet - Using revEmu (v9.8.1 R4) - Working Dedicated and Listen server (Steam & Non-Steam) - HLTV is also included and works - Half-Life (Multiplayer) included - Half-Life maps are totally removed - Support for unicode input - Ingame ads are removed INSTALL NOTES: 1] Install the game from setup 2] Run game from desktop shortcut 3] Done, Enjoy Please, SEED!
